BdmRwoiBxEA.title: In the Mith (original Mix)
BdmRwoiBxEA.description:
BIO
Emil De la Cruz`s Obsession for electronic music specially Techno is a growing Monster. Starting out as hip-hop producer right after propellerheads launched REASON 2.0 in the year 2000 he has been able to convert his musical ideas into reality. After years of producing hip-hop music for the local artist in Bern (Switzerland) and for himself, he was introduced to the electronic music by a friend of his, who used to listen to electronic music at this time. Even though he wasn’t too familiar with electronic music at this point, he decided to produce a track for his friend, and that was the day that turned his musical career around. Since that day Emil de la Cruz has been evolving into the electronic music world and he continues to improve his skills as an electronic music producer day by day. Nowadays Emil De la Cruz is developing his new passion, which is performing his tracks as DJ. The only mission he has in mind is to bring Techno to all the corners of this world.

.
